<doc id="1181544" wikidata="Q112207" url="?curid=1181544" title="Villanuova sul Clisi">
<text>Villanuova sul Clisi (Brescian: ) is a &quot;comune&quot; in the province of Brescia, in Lombardy, Italy. It is situated on the left bank of the river Chiese, known locally as &quot;Clisi&quot;. As of 2011 Villanuova sul Clisi had a population of 5,837.

==Sister city==
Villanuova sul Clisi is twinned with:
* Trébeurden, France, since 2000.

