<doc id="1181620" wikidata="Q7101988" url="?curid=1181620" title="Organization of Sikkimese Unity">
<text>Organization of Sikkimese Unity, a political organization in the Indian state of Sikkim. OSU was founded in 1994 to fight for the reinstallment of reservation quotas for the Nepali-speaking majority of the state. The general secretary of OSU is Jigme N Kazi.
